resources.string:
Hi My name is Sanchita. 

 I love working. 

 I just cannot sit idle, I have a tendency of keeping myself occupied in one thing or another all the time. 
 There are times when I think why does a day have 24 hours!! I mean what is a person supposed to do with so much of time and then there are times when I think why does a day have only 24 hours 
 I love my busy life, it keeps me self occupied and even a pandemic or lockdown did not make me feel bored or depressed 
 I would suggest everyone to keep learning and exploring as there is so much to do!!
